      "widgets_values": ["CraftKit × SeedVR2 — Smart Upscale\n\nPattern:\n1. SmartResolutionMultiplier calculates the 2× target resolution from the input image automatically\n2. ImageScaleBy pre-downscales the input (0.75×) so SeedVR2 has room to work\n3. SeedVR2 upscales to the computed target resolution (connected from SmartResolutionMultiplier → resolution)\n4. SmartResize normalizes the output to a consistent longest side\n\nChange multiplier on SmartResolutionMultiplier to control the upscale factor. Change longest_side on SmartResize to control output size."],
